<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//WAPFORUM//DTD XHTML Mobile 1.0//EN" "http://www.wapforum.org/DTD/xhtml-mobile10.dtd">
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=0" />
    <link href="{:C('STATIC_ROOT')}/activity/hot_event/css/basic.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <link href="{:C('STATIC_ROOT')}/activity/hot_event/css/style.css?=v20160801" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <title>票票喵</title>

</head>
<body>
    <section>
        <!--正文-->
        <div class="invite_pic">
            <img src="{:C('STATIC_ROOT')}/activity/hot_event/images/01.jpg" />
        </div>
        <div class="invite_square">
            <div class="invite_world ">
                <p>利率风暴即将来临，爆款抢购活动，将在2016年08月02日至2016年08月06日时间段内开启超高利率让你赚翻天。</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="invite_pic" style="margin-top:-1px;">
            <img src="{:C('STATIC_ROOT')}/activity/hot_event/images/02.jpg" />
        </div>
        <div class="invite_time">
            <div class="invite_number">
                <div class="invite_left cut10 fl">
                    <img src="{:C('STATIC_ROOT')}/activity/hot_event/images/05_03.png" />
                </div>
                <div class="invite_right cut90 fl">
                    <p>活动期间，每人每天限购爆款次数不设上限，每次投资数额不设上限，投资期限1~3个月。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="clear"></div>
            <div class="invite_number">
                <div class="invite_left cut10 fl">
                    <img src="{:C('STATIC_ROOT')}/activity/hot_event/images/05_06.png" style="padding-top:20px;"/>
                </div>
                <div class="invite_right cut90 fl">
                    <p style="padding-top:20px;">
                        每天只在4个时段可参与爆款抢购活动，每次
                        抢购时长仅为1小时，抢购时段分别为 8:30、
                        10:00、17:00和 20:00。
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="clear"></div>
        <div class="invite_footer tc" style="margin-top:-1px;">
            <p>最终解释权归票票喵所有</p>
            <p>如有任何疑问请拨打在线客服热线：400-992-8855 </p>
        </div>


		
        <div class="invite_now tc" style="cursor:pointer;" onclick="go2App()" >
            <p>立即抢购</p>
        </div>

    </section>
    
    <script type="text/javascript">
    
    	var u = navigator.userAgent, app = navigator.appVersion;
    	var isAndroid = u.indexOf('Android') > -1 || u.indexOf('Linux') > -1; //android终端或者uc浏览器
    	var isiOS = !!u.match(/\(i[^;]+;( U;)? CPU.+Mac OS X/); //ios终端
    	
	    function go2App(){
	    	if(isAndroid == true) {
	    		ppm.toAction(2);
	    	} else if(isiOS == true) {
	    		loadURL('skip2');
	    	}
	    	return;
	    }
	    
	    function loadURL(url) {
	        var iFrame;
	        iFrame = document.createElement("iframe");
	        iFrame.setAttribute("src", url);
	        iFrame.setAttribute("style", "display:none;");
	        iFrame.setAttribute("height", "0px");
	        iFrame.setAttribute("width", "0px");
	        iFrame.setAttribute("frameborder", "0");
	        document.body.appendChild(iFrame);
	        iFrame.parentNode.removeChild(iFrame);
	        iFrame = null;
	    }
	    
    </script>
    
</body>
</html>